## Vulnerable Pipeline

```groovy
// No provenance generated
stage('Build and Push') {
    steps {
        sh """
            docker build -t ${IMAGE_NAME}:${BUILD_NUMBER} .
            docker push ${IMAGE_NAME}:${BUILD_NUMBER}
        """
        // GAP: no record of who built this, from which commit,
        // on which Jenkins node, at what time
    }
}
```

Without provenance:
```bash
cosign verify-attestation \
    --key cosign.pub \
    --type slsaprovenance \
    123456789012.dkr.ecr.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/webapp:v1.0.0

# Error: no matching attestations: no attestations found for type slsaprovenance
```

