### Jenkins Environment Variables Available for Provenance

```groovy
// These are available in any Jenkins pipeline
env.BUILD_NUMBER          // Jenkins build number
env.BUILD_URL             // Full URL to this build
env.GIT_COMMIT            // Bitbucket commit SHA
env.GIT_BRANCH            // Branch name
env.JOB_NAME              // Pipeline job name
env.BUILD_TIMESTAMP       // Build start time (with Timestamper plugin)
env.NODE_NAME             // Jenkins build node name
```

