## What Provenance Proves

| Question | Without Provenance | With Provenance |
|----------|-------------------|-----------------|
| Built by CI? | Unknown | Yes — Jenkins job URL in attestation |
| Which commit? | Unknown | SHA from Bitbucket |
| Which branch? | Unknown | Branch name recorded |
| Who triggered? | Unknown | Jenkins build user |
| When? | Unknown | Build timestamps |
| Same build reproducible? | No | Known (reproducible: false in predicate) |

